{"title":"Set the alarm for 22:00","description":"Turn on the alarm clock on 22:00 with sound. 22 hours   alarm clock. Free and simple alarm online. Set alarm for 22 hours  .","content":"Is there a need to set an alarm for 22 hours  ? Use our simple and free alarm clock online! \nSet the alarm for 22 hours   or choose another time by setting it yourself or by selecting from the list. An alarm clock with a sound that you can set yourself. After setting the time, press the **Add** button to turn on the alarm.\n\nTurn on the alarm clock for 22 hours   and go about your business, the alarm clock will definitely notify you at exactly 22:00.\n\nAll alarms are saved in your browser, so you can reuse them. The clock beautifully shows the time remaining from 22 hours  , with an accuracy of seconds and milliseconds."}